title: Week 16 Waivers 2021
description:
Field Yates, Matthew Berry, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp recap Monday Night Football, preview the pair of games for tonight to finish Week 15 and look ahead to the players you need to add from the waiver wire in Week 16. Plus, key injury and COVID protocol updates from around the NFL.
